or the same individual.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":257,"html":258},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 45.1393 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Nenci 1995 1183 no.2 tav.267.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001415\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Nenci 1997 1191-1192 tav.234.2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001729\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001729\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> De Vido 2003 400 no.12 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 2008 87 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000160\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000160\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G27 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":260,"html":261},"handnote","\u003Cp>The letters are somewhat worn, but present a regular and wide/square module, broadly and deeply incised. Alpha with straight bar, epsilon with shorter middle bar, omicron smaller and above the line, rho with a small closed eye.\u003C/p> Line 1  13-17 (13 = omicron)  Interlineation line 1 to 2    ",{"id":263,"html":264},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[266,268,271,272],{"html":267},"Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\u003C/a>",{"id":269,"lang":133,"html":270},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div